Package com.github.errantlinguist.jtextgrid

Class Summary
Entry<D> A single entry in the TextGrid file, representing either an interval or a point on a tier.
TextGridFile<T> A representation of a Praat TextGrid file and the annotation data contained therein.
TextGridFileReader<T> A file reader which reads in Praat TextGrid files, parses the data contained therein, and returns it as a TextGridFile object representing it.
Tier<D> A tier in a TextGrid file.
TimeSeriesData<T extends TimeSeriesData<?>> An object representing data associated with a time sequence.
TimeSeriesDataCollection<E,T extends TimeSeriesDataCollection<?,?>> A Collection-like object which contains multiple TimeSeriesData objects.
 

Enum Summary
Tier.TierClass The TextGrid tier class, e.g. "IntervalTier" or "TextTier", as defined in the TextGrid file itself.
